		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I feel like we are getting close to having a Release Candidate ROM soon, So I've been thinking about the theme topic lately. There has been mentions about deciding on a themed volume title, but I never saw a clear consensus yet.<br /><br />Suggestions I found so far:<br /><div class="quotetitle">Myask in <a href="https://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?p=192404#p192404" class="postlink">Action 53 volume 3</a> wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Action 53 Function Ceiling ⅓  (Action 53/3 for short) <br />[…54/3 = 18 = round(53/3)= ceil(53/3)]<br />Action 53…<span style="font-size: 90%; line-height: normal">3…</span><span style="font-size: 80%; line-height: normal">3…</span><span style="font-size: 70%; line-height: normal">3…</span><span style="font-size: 60%; line-height: normal">3…</span><span style="font-size: 50%; line-height: normal">3…</span><span style="font-size: 40%; line-height: normal">3…</span><br />Action 53 3: Too Hot For the Kitchen <br />JAN CTION PON 53</div><br />I personally like the first suggestion here but here's one of my own. <br /><br />Action 53 Episode 3: Revenge of the Twins<br /><br />This was thought up due to the compo winner, the 4 mojon twins games, and referencing a popular lackluster movie.

		

